@host = http://localhost:5050

### Create a product (interceptor stamps CreatedAtUtc + CreatedBy)
POST {{host}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: mukesh

{
  "name": "Keyboard",
  "price": 49.99
}

### Update a product (interceptor stamps UpdatedAtUtc + UpdatedBy)
PUT {{host}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: alice

{
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "price": 89.99
}

### List products (soft-deleted rows hidden by the global query filter)
GET {{host}}/products

### Soft delete a product (interceptor turns DELETE into UPDATE)
DELETE {{host}}/products/1

### List soft-deleted products (IgnoreQueryFilters bypasses the filter)
GET {{host}}/products/deleted
